summary:
Leading a COPE¬∞ working group on psychological safety, bullying, sexual assault and harassment in the maritime sector. 

Serving as an IMO Policy Coordinator for the Commonwealth of Dominica Maritime Registry: an open international ship registry committed to serving the seafaring community as a whole through training, licensing and certification with integrity and honesty. 

Connecting maritime professionals, in order for them to benefit from the online learning simulators, training, examination platforms NEMO¬∞ and HALO¬∞ developed by Northeast Maritime Institute.

Working as dual-licensed maritime officer, Eva Lianne started her career by crossing the many oceans of our globe on large container vessels. 

#leadwithlove #honorthemariner
